public class RevokeRequest extends ASN1Object
 RevokeRequest ::= SEQUENCE {
     issuerName            Name,
     serialNumber          INTEGER,
     reason                CRLReason,
     invalidityDate         GeneralizedTime OPTIONAL,
     passphrase            OCTET STRING OPTIONAL,
     comment               UTF8String OPTIONAL }
